WEBVTT

07:10.830 --> 07:12.231
So then
they told me to make it like

07:12.298 --> 07:13.733
the poker-game episode
of the Batman cartoon

07:13.800 --> 07:15.735
where the bad guys
tell stories about Batman.

07:15.802 --> 07:17.837
Then they kept telling me
it "needed something."

07:17.937 --> 07:19.672
Yeah, no shit,
it needed something!

07:19.772 --> 07:22.842
It needed to never be pitched!
I did my job!
